  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Genome
    A Genome maintains an ordered list of triangles that are stored as float arrays.
    TriangleGenerator
    This class is used to create triangles that are represented by a single float array containing 10 genes.
    TriangleManager
    The TriangleManager takes a float array from a TriangleGenerator and allows you to extract data from it in a much more convenient way.
